Siluetti

A primitive horizontal-vertical-type solver for black and white nonograms.
Written in Haskell.

Licenced under the terms of GNU GPL v3+. See COPYING.

Author: Joel Lehtonen, joel.lehtonen Ã¤t jyu.fi

There are two examples in a file called Examples.hs.

- "football" can not be solved with horizontal-vertical solver
- "dog" can be solved with this thing.

Try by yourself:

$ runhaskell Example.hs

More information about nonograms: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nonogram
